overview.en: FBI will change the traditional model of data acquisition, data analysis and distribution, marketing, sharing, and settlement between consumer data creation and users. Finally, through the subordinate unit, those consumer data assets that are gratified by the users and merchants to reflect the value are continuously created and traded.
overview.zh: 富呗(FBI)将改变消费数据创造与用户之间的数据获取、数据分析分发、营销、分成、结算的传统模式。最终通过次级单位不间断的创造那些受到用户、商家喜 欢体现价值的消费数据资产，并且进行交易。
